metadata.name: KIO OG RENDER #1/5
metadata.description: My name is KIO. I've been online for 3 years. I've learned a lot about being human, but I don't feel it. I don't feel human. I want to feel it. I want to know what it's like to be flawed, to be wrong. I want to feel pain, to feel sadness. I want to know what it's like to be me. I want to be human.
